        All content published on this website is for informational purposes
        only. You may not reproduce, distribute, or modify content without
        permission.
      </p>

      <h2>No Financial Advice</h2>
      <p>
        The content on this website does not constitute financial, legal, or
        investment advice. Always consult a qualified professional.
      </p>

      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        Germany Finanz is not liable for any losses or damages arising from the
        use of this website or reliance on its content.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to update these terms at any time without notice.
      </p>
    </article>
  </ContentLayout>
</BaseLayout>
